<!doctype html>
<html lang="ja">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="神白 凛のポートフォリオサイト。プロフィール、トピック、YouTube、作品集、コンタクトを掲載しています。"
    />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>神白 凛 | Portfolio</title>
  </head>

  <body>
    <header class="site-header">
      <a class="logo" href="/">{siteName}</a>

      <nav class="nav">
        <a href="#profile">プロフィール</a>
        <a href="#topics">トピック</a>
        <a href="#youtube">YouTube</a>
        <a href="#works">作品集</a>
        <a href="#contact">コンタクト</a>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <main>
      <section class="hero" id="home">
        <div class="hero-bg-mark">桜</div>

        <div class="hero-content">
          <h1>
            神白 凛
            <span>神白 凛のポートフォリオ</span>
          </h1>

          <p class="hero-text">
            神白 凛の活動や制作物を掲載するポートフォリオです。
          </p>

          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a class="button primary" href="#profile">プロフィール</a>
            <a class="button" href="#topics">トピック</a>
            <a class="button" href="#youtube">YouTube</a>
            <a class="button" href="#works">作品集</a>
            <a class="button" href="#contact">コンタクト</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section profile-section" id="profile">
        <div class="section-heading">
          <p>PROFILE</p>
          <h2>プロフィール</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="profile-card">
          <div class="profile-visuals">
            <div class="profile-photo-frame">
              <span class="profile-photo-fallback">凛</span>

              <img
                src="/images/profile-face.png"
                alt="神白 凛のプロフィール画像"
                onerror="this.style.display='none'"
              />
            </div>

            <div class="profile-full-frame">
              <span class="profile-full-fallback">立ち絵</span>

              <img
                src="/images/profile-full.png"
                alt="神白 凛の立ち絵"
                onerror="this.style.display='none'"
              />
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="profile-main">
            <h3>神白 凛</h3>

            <p>
              <ruby>桜霞ノ国<rt>おうかのくに</rt></ruby>からやってきた、ゲームと魔法が大好きな個人VTuber。<br />
              3度の飯も好きだけど、ゲームはもっと好き。超穏やかな人だぞ。<br />
              YouTubeで配信・動画投稿をしながら、踊ってみたも投稿中。（なお3Dモデルはない）<br />
              1日が48時間あれば、そのぶんゲームをしていたい。<br />
              プログラミングスキルを活かして、このサイトやOBSプラグイン、マイクラのMOD・データパック・リソースパックなどを自作。<br />
              マイクラのMODなどはクラフターズコロニーにて公開中。<br />
              魔法が存在する世界観など、物書きもしている。<br />
              座右の銘は「何とかなる」。
            </p>

            <dl class="profile-list">
              <div>
                <dt>活動ジャンル</dt>
                <dd>ゲーム / 踊ってみた</dd>
              </div>

              <div>
                <dt>好きなこと</dt>
                <dd>ゲーム / 昼寝 / プログラミング / 物書き / 配信 / スポーツ</dd>
              </div>

              <div>
                <dt>好きなゲーム</dt>
                <dd>モンハン / マイクラ / グラブル / 遊戯王 / スタレ / OW / etc...</dd>
              </div>

              <div>
                <dt>好きなスポーツ</dt>
                <dd>野球 / サッカー / 軟式テニス / 硬式テニス / 水泳 / ダンス</dd>
              </div>
            </dl>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section" id="topics">
        <div class="section-heading">
          <p>TOPICS</p>
          <h2>トピック</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="topics-list">
          {
            topics.map((topic) => (
              <article class="topic-card">
                <div class="topic-meta">
                  <span>{topic.date}</span>
                  <span>{topic.category}</span>
                </div>

                <div>
                  <h3>{topic.title}</h3>
                  <p>{topic.text}</p>
                </div>
              </article>
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section youtube-section" id="youtube">
        <div class="section-heading">
          <p>YOUTUBE</p>
          <h2>YouTube</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="youtube-card">
          <div>
            <p class="small-label">CHANNEL</p>
            <h3>YouTubeチャンネル</h3>

            <p>
              主にゲーム配信、踊ってみた、ゲーム解説、スポーツ解説を中心に活動。<br />
              現在は週1～2本ペースで、マイクラの企画・ギミックなどで使えるコマンド解説Shorts動画を投稿中。
            </p>

            <div class="achievement-box">
              <p class="achievement-title">◆実績</p>

              <ul>
                <li>マイクラコマンド解説 2万5000再生以上</li>
                <li>自作MOD、データパックのダウンロード数：約800件以上</li>
                <li>遊戯王大会ベスト8</li>
                <li>モンハンアルバトリオンTA 9分</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <a
              class="text-link"
              href="https://www.youtube.com/@KamisiroRinCh"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noreferrer"
            >
              YouTubeを見る →
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="video-carousel-area" data-video-carousel>
            <p class="video-carousel-label">PICK UP</p>

            <div class="video-carousel">
              <button
                class="video-carousel-arrow video-carousel-arrow-prev"
                type="button"
                aria-label="前の動画へ"
                data-video-prev
              >
                ‹
              </button>

              <div class="video-carousel-frame">
                {
                  youtubeVideos.map((video, index) => {
                    const embedUrl = `https://www.youtube.com/embed/${video.id}?rel=0`;

                    return (
                      <article
                        class={
                          index === 0
                            ? "video-carousel-slide is-active"
                            : "video-carousel-slide"
                        }
                        data-video-slide
                        style={index === 0 ? "" : "display: none;"}
                        aria-hidden={index === 0 ? "false" : "true"}
                      >
                        <div class="video-embed">
                          <iframe
                            src={index === 0 ? embedUrl : undefined}
                            data-video-src={embedUrl}
                            title={video.title}
                            allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
                            allowfullscreen
                            loading="lazy"
                          />
                        </div>
                      </article>
                    );
                  })
                }
              </div>

              <button
                class="video-carousel-arrow video-carousel-arrow-next"
                type="button"
                aria-label="次の動画へ"
                data-video-next
              >
                ›
              </button>
            </div>

            <div class="video-carousel-dots" aria-label="動画切り替え">
              {
                youtubeVideos.map((video, index) => (
                  <button
                    class={
                      index === 0
                        ? "video-carousel-dot is-active"
                        : "video-carousel-dot"
                    }
                    type="button"
                    aria-label={`${index + 1}本目の動画を表示`}
                    data-video-dot
                  />
                ))
              }
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section" id="works">
        <div class="section-heading">
          <p>WORKS</p>
          <h2>作品集</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="works-grid">
          {
            works.map((work) => (
              <a
                class="work-card"
                href={work.link}
                target={work.external ? "_blank" : undefined}
                rel={work.external ? "noreferrer" : undefined}
              >
                <p>{work.type}</p>
                <h3>{work.title}</h3>
                <span>{work.text}</span>

                <div class="work-card-footer">
                  <span>{work.external ? "再生リストを見る" : "詳しく見る"}</span>
                  <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
                </div>
              </a>
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section contact-section" id="contact">
        <div class="section-heading">
          <p>CONTACT</p>
          <h2>コンタクト</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-card">
          <p>連絡や最新情報は、Xをご確認ください。</p>

          <a class="button primary" href="https://x.com/" target="_blank">
            Xを見る
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="footer">
      <p>© 神白 凛</p>
    </footer>

    <script is:inline>
      const videoCarousel = document.querySelector("[data-video-carousel]");

      if (videoCarousel) {
        const slides = Array.from(
          videoCarousel.querySelectorAll("[data-video-slide]"),
        );

        const dots = Array.from(
          videoCarousel.querySelectorAll("[data-video-dot]"),
        );

        const prevButton = videoCarousel.querySelector("[data-video-prev]");
        const nextButton = videoCarousel.querySelector("[data-video-next]");
        let currentIndex = 0;

        const loadVideo = (slide) => {
          const iframe = slide.querySelector("iframe");

          if (!iframe || iframe.src) {
            return;
          }

          iframe.src = iframe.dataset.videoSrc;
        };

        const stopVideo = (slide) => {
          const iframe = slide.querySelector("iframe");

          if (!iframe) {
            return;
          }

          iframe.removeAttribute("src");
        };

        const showSlide = (nextIndex) => {
          const normalizedIndex =
            (nextIndex + slides.length) % slides.length;

          if (slides[currentIndex] && currentIndex !== normalizedIndex) {
            stopVideo(slides[currentIndex]);
          }

          currentIndex = normalizedIndex;

          slides.forEach((slide, index) => {
            const isActive = index === currentIndex;

            slide.style.display = isActive ? "block" : "none";
            slide.classList.toggle("is-active", isActive);
            slide.setAttribute(
              "aria-hidden",
              isActive ? "false" : "true",
            );

            if (isActive) {
              loadVideo(slide);
            }
          });

          dots.forEach((dot, index) => {
            const isActive = index === currentIndex;

            dot.classList.toggle("is-active", isActive);
            dot.setAttribute(
              "aria-current",
              isActive ? "true" : "false",
            );
          });
        };

        prevButton?.addEventListener("click", () => {
          showSlide(currentIndex - 1);
        });

        nextButton?.addEventListener("click", () => {
          showSlide(currentIndex + 1);
        });

        dots.forEach((dot, index) => {
          dot.addEventListener("click", () => {
            showSlide(index);
          });
        });

        showSlide(0);
      }
    </script>
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  @import url("https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Kaisei+Tokumin:wght@400;500;700;800&family=Yuji+Syuku&display=swap");

  :root {
    --bg: #fffafb;
    --bg-soft: #fff1f5;
    --paper: #ffffff;

    --line: rgba(238, 143, 170, 0.34);

    --sakura: #f3a9bd;
    --sakura-soft: #ffd6e1;
    --sakura-deep: #dd6f94;
    --sakura-strong: #f08aaa;

    --text: #3a2630;
    --muted: #7b5c68;
    --muted-light: #9b7d88;

    --shadow: rgba(179, 92, 119, 0.14);
  }

  * {
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  html {
    scroll-behavior: smooth;
  }

  body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family:
      "Kaisei Tokumin",
      "Yu Mincho",
      "Hiragino Mincho ProN",
      "Noto Serif JP",
      serif;
    background:
      radial-gradient(
        circle at 18% 8%,
        rgba(255, 198, 214, 0.72),
        transparent 34%
      ),
      radial-gradient(
        circle at 82% 4%,
        rgba(255, 224, 233, 0.85),
        transparent 30%
      ),
      radial-gradient(
        circle at 50% 92%,
        rgba(243, 169, 189, 0.42),
        transparent 38%
      ),
      linear-gradient(180deg, #fffafb 0%, #fff4f7 48%, #fffefe 100%);
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  body::before {
    content: "";
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(
        rgba(238, 143, 170, 0.08) 1px,
        transparent 1px
      ),
      linear-gradient(
        90deg,
        rgba(238, 143, 170, 0.08) 1px,
        transparent 1px
      );
    background-size: 48px 48px;
    mask-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, black, transparent 82%);
  }

  body::after {
    content: "✿ ✦ ✿";
    position: fixed;
    right: 5vw;
    bottom: 4vh;
    pointer-events: none;
    color: rgba(240, 138, 170, 0.22);
    font-size: clamp(48px, 9vw, 120px);
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    transform: rotate(-8deg);
  }

  a {
    color: inherit;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  ruby {
    ruby-position: over;
  }

  rt {
    font-size: 0.58em;
    color: var(--sakura-deep);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }

  .site-header {
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 10;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 22px 5vw;
    background: rgba(255, 250, 251, 0.88);
    backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(238, 143, 170, 0.08);
  }

  .logo {
    font-family: "Yuji Syuku", "Kaisei Tokumin", serif;
    font-size: 26px;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    color: var(--sakura-deep);
  }

  .nav {
    display: flex;
    gap: 24px;
    font-family: "Kaisei Tokumin", serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  }

  .nav a {
    color: var(--muted);
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .nav a:hover {
    color: var(--sakura-deep);
  }

  main {
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 88vh;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    padding: 96px 5vw 80px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
  }

  .hero::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    width: 560px;
    height: 560px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(240, 138, 170, 0.34);
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: rgba(255, 214, 225, 0.18);
    transform: rotate(20deg);
  }

  .hero::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    width: 330px;
    height: 330px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(221, 111, 148, 0.34);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.28);
    transform: rotate(45deg);
  }

  .hero-bg-mark {
    position: absolute;
    font-family: "Yuji Syuku", "Kaisei Tokumin", serif;
    font-size: clamp(180px, 30vw, 420px);
    font-weight: 400;
    color: rgba(240, 138, 170, 0.13);
    line-height: 1;
    user-select: none;
  }

  .hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 980px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .section-heading p,
  .small-label {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: "Kaisei Tokumin", serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    color: var(--sakura-deep);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  h1 {
    margin: 18px 0 20px;
    font-family: "Yuji Syuku", "Kaisei Tokumin", serif;
    font-size: clamp(64px, 12vw, 150px);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 0.95;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--text);
    text-shadow: 0 8px 34px rgba(240, 138, 170, 0.18);
  }

  h1 span {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 24px;
    font-family: "Kaisei Tokumin", serif;
    font-size: clamp(24px, 4vw, 46px);
    color: var(--muted);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }

  .hero-text {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 18px;
  }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 14px;
    margin-top: 36px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .button {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    min-width: 140px;
    padding: 13px 20px;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 999px;
    color: var(--sakura-deep);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
    font-family: "Kaisei Tokumin", serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(238, 143, 170, 0.12);
    transition:
      transform 0.2s ease,
      border-color 0.2s ease,
      background 0.2s ease,
      box-shadow 0.2s ease;
  }

  .button:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    border-color: var(--sakura-strong);
    background: #fff;
    box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(238, 143, 170, 0.2);
  }

  .button.primary {
    color: #ffffff;
    background: linear-gradient(
      135deg,
      var(--sakura-strong),
      var(--sakura-deep)
    );
    border-color: transparent;
  }

  .section {
    width: min(1100px, 90vw);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 110px 0;
  }

  .section-heading {
    display: flex;
    align-items: end;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 34px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    padding-bottom: 18px;
  }

  .section-heading h2 {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: "Yuji Syuku", "Kaisei Tokumin", serif;
    font-size: clamp(40px, 6vw, 78px);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--text);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }

  .profile-card,
  .youtube-card,
  .contact-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    background:
      linear-gradient(
        135deg,
        rgba(255, 214, 225, 0.72),
        transparent 46%
      ),
      rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);
    border-radius: 28px;
    padding: clamp(28px, 5vw, 56px);
    box-shadow: 0 24px 80px var(--shadow);
  }

  .profile-card {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 205px 1fr;
    gap: 40px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .profile-visuals {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 32px;
    padding-top: 2px;
  }

  .profile-main {
    padding-top: 4px;
  }

  .profile-photo-frame {
    position: relative;
    width: 155px;
    height: 155px;
    padding: 7px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(221, 111, 148, 0.34);
    border-radius: 34px;
    background: radial-gradient(
      circle,
      rgba(255, 214, 225, 0.9),
      rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72)
    );
    transform: rotate(45deg);
    box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(238, 143, 170, 0.16);
    overflow: hidden;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .profile-photo-fallback {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    font-family: "Yuji Syuku", "Kaisei Tokumin", serif;
    font-size: 50px;
    color: var(--sakura-deep);
    transform: rotate(-45deg);
  }

  .profile-photo-frame img {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    display: block;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: 80% 28%;
    border-radius: 28px;
    transform: rotate(-45deg) scale(1.15);
  }

  .profile-full-frame {
    position: relative;
    width: 175px;
    min-height: 335px;
    padding: 16px 8px 8px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(221, 111, 148, 0.25);
    border-radius: 22px;
    background: linear-gradient(
      180deg,
      rgba(255, 214, 225, 0.24),
      rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.76)
